 discovery of\nfundamental laws of science and believe that our work is an important step\ntowards automating the scientific method.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 Sep 2021 17:19:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 8 Oct 2021 15:08:54 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 4 Aug 2022 12:08:29 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 9 Jan 2023 12:19:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-10"}
