 the turbulent dissipation\nparameter that when the turbulence is initially low, is found to be in good\nagreement with previous estimate of non self-gravitating supersonic turbulence.\nabridged.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 4 Sep 2021 12:49:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-03"}
